Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.84,0:00:07.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然突然下午修校
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.62,0:00:13.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來遙今天便當做得格外賣力呀 是為了大兔君？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.98,0:00:18.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…不是的 只是偶然起早了而已
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.99,0:00:21.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遙
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.93,0:00:24.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的不是你想的那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.03,0:00:36.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大兔有吃便當嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.57,0:00:49.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大兔
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.33,0:00:49.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.56,0:00:53.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第三次嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.15,0:00:56.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底出什麼事了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.78,0:01:02.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魔法？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.30,0:01:06.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 和我使用的魔法一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.62,0:01:08.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和希梅亞一樣是…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.44,0:01:12.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是叫上古魔法師嗎 那是怎麼回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.61,0:01:18.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道 但總之很不妙
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.93,0:01:19.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.13,0:01:25.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,離我可以死亡的次數恢復還有10分多一點
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.60,0:01:28.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得盡量小心不要死掉才行 那麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.44,0:01:30.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回學生會室吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.99,0:01:36.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去問問那個讓人火大的學生會長到底發生了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.28,0:01:37.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼做很晦氣就是了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.69,0:02:01.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 我說了鏘鏘吧 為什麼無視我呀
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.28,0:02:07.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,破除一切力量的凶劍
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.85,0:02:10.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.12,0:02:16.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那把劍唯一不能發揮力量的對象
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.71,0:02:20.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有天魔的使者——天使們
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.59,0:02:22.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美雷
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.94,0:02:25.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道天魔嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.10,0:02:27.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.05,0:02:44.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你不掂量自己而非要養著那個女人的話
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.41,0:02:46.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就給你一句忠告吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.44,0:02:49.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小心從月亮而來的侵蝕
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.06,0:02:52.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.83,0:02:57.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日向那混蛋 居然說我不可能養得了希梅亞
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.15,0:03:00.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我就來證明他是錯的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.00,0:03:05.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼要吻我？為什麼要吻我？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.78,0:03:06.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,閉嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.01,0:03:12.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,詛咒解除了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.64,0:03:13.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,活力百倍
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.70,0:03:15.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安度的米蕾
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.28,0:03:18.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敵人來了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.06,0:03:22.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是剛那天魔的同伴嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.06,0:03:24.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是BOSS呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.19,0:03:26.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好膽量
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.19,0:03:38.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這什麼東西？！好厲害 月光快點快點
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.14,0:03:40.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來是人類能夠活動的空間
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.43,0:03:46.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就去看看吧 畢竟是對方的招待
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.28,0:05:28.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,月光那傢伙 關鍵時刻跑哪偷懶去了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.81,0:05:37.80,Title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fade(500,0)\be10\pos(238,122)}「天魔之名仍未吟誦」
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.21,0:05:31.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.01,0:05:33.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.05,0:05:35.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺很不妙呀
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.86,0:05:37.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敵人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.22,0:05:45.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經被殺死3次了 明顯是抱有敵意的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.71,0:05:59.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼辦？不攀上那裡是無法去到學生會室的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.77,0:06:01.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咱們戰鬥的話 能贏嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.45,0:06:02.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.04,0:06:04.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希梅亞？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.35,0:06:07.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 希梅亞 你去哪了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.86,0:06:10.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希梅亞
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.47,0:06:26.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以過來
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.46,0:06:35.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.88,0:06:37.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第四次嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.60,0:06:44.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希梅亞
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.41,0:06:45.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以過來
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.97,0:06:46.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要過來
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.10,0:06:51.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要…不要看這樣的我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.46,0:06:53.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬上就救你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.91,0:06:56.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 不要
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.32,0:06:58.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.47,0:07:04.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手 你那麼想要我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.92,0:07:08.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希梅亞
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.97,0:07:12.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明好不容易才見到大兔
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.06,0:07:16.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不想再與大兔分開…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.32,0:07:18.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我馬上就救你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.90,0:07:19.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大兔
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.02,0:07:30.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.47,0:07:39.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.77,0:07:40.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希梅亞
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.20,0:07:47.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,賽托希梅亞 沒想到你愛上的就是這種無聊的人類
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.79,0:07:52.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你為了這種渣滓而拋棄了我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.41,0:07:58.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,究竟發生了什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.58,0:08:01.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,與你無關的事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.28,0:08:06.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…不是希梅亞
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.09,0:08:09.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大兔
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.70,0:08:12.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.56,0:08:20.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想想 這是第6次死了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.08,0:08:24.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再殺一次的話這傢伙就活不過來了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.58,0:08:27.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.36,0:08:31.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手 巴爾思庫拉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.90,0:09:03.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要走了 巴爾思庫拉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.67,0:09:08.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你喜歡那傢伙嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.69,0:09:15.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼要選那種傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.80,0:09:22.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他只是個人類啊 愚蠢渺小的人類啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.53,0:09:28.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但…但至少沒有我們這般…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.20,0:09:29.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,污穢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.06,0:09:31.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你才不污穢…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.24,0:09:34.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真溫柔呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.50,0:09:37.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一直都狠溫柔
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.48,0:09:43.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但看看這污穢的身體吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.05,0:09:50.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看看這滿是污穢的身體吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.31,0:09:59.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在過於長久的孤獨中
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.88,0:10:04.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被侵蝕得越來越黑暗、骯髒
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.62,0:10:13.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是因為月亮變圓與缺 詛咒就會加深
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.02,0:10:22.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經太過痛楚 太過寂寞
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.92,0:10:28.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以要結束才行 巴爾思庫拉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.24,0:10:32.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想要陪在你身邊直至最後
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.10,0:10:39.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伴我一起度過最後時光的人 我希望自己選擇
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.97,0:10:43.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是那個人類？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.56,0:10:50.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要為了那種人類死去嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.64,0:10:52.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.89,0:10:55.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你錯了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.47,0:10:58.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是呢 我也這麼想
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.36,0:11:02.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是巴爾思庫拉 我真的對他…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.81,0:11:08.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的愛著大兔 那已經是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.32,0:11:15.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使永恆的此身灰飛煙滅也在所不惜
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.96,0:11:24.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希梅亞被叫巴爾思庫拉的傢伙佔據了身體嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.37,0:11:29.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該怎麼做 怎麼做才能把他扯出你的身體？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.32,0:11:31.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你開什麼玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.00,0:11:35.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,橫刀奪走了她的心的是你呀人類！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.95,0:11:54.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是我的 漂亮的賽托希梅亞是只屬於我的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.92,0:11:59.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我要帶走她 去到你無法觸及的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.90,0:12:09.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去到你絕對無法觸及的只屬於我和她的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.23,0:12:09.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.57,0:12:16.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大兔 快跑
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.78,0:12:21.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趁我壓制住他的這段時間 快跑
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.62,0:12:24.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.61,0:12:25.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希梅亞
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.12,0:12:29.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好 又要壓制不住了…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.63,0:12:31.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快跑
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.47,0:12:35.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在我跑掉的話 你就會像9年前那樣被這傢伙帶走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.42,0:12:37.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我怎麼能自己跑掉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.52,0:12:43.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求你了大兔 聽話 我已經保護不了你了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.34,0:12:47.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想你死啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.16,0:12:49.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要是死了的話我…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.13,0:12:51.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希梅亞
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.63,0:12:59.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定…我一定回來救你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.58,0:13:01.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡 可惡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.15,0:13:05.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我到底怎麼回事 為什麼每次都什麼也做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.45,0:13:09.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,賽托希梅亞 你為了那種渣滓…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.72,0:13:11.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太礙眼了 去死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.55,0:13:28.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種程度給我撐住
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.50,0:13:39.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大兔
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.87,0:13:44.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉遙 學生會長叫我 突然有工作
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.27,0:13:49.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,便當謝謝了 我過會兒吃
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.74,0:13:53.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣呀 既然是學生會的工作就沒辦法了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.29,0:13:58.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好想見你 好想見你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.69,0:14:01.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平凡可能確實也不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.90,0:14:03.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遙
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.12,0:14:36.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遙？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.09,0:14:41.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大兔 現在方便嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.09,0:14:44.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…有點…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.95,0:14:45.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大兔？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.28,0:14:48.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事吧 發生什麼了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.29,0:14:53.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事都沒有 不要擔心 話說有什麼事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.53,0:14:59.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是算了 你好像在忙呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.46,0:15:01.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.25,0:15:07.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶 大兔 雖然我不知道發生了什麼 但別太亂來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.58,0:15:10.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還記得嗎 在學空手道的那會兒
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.95,0:15:14.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你曾多次和比你大的人對著幹吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.39,0:15:16.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直弄到遍體鱗傷
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.41,0:15:21.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但沒有逃避
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.16,0:15:26.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂？怎麼了 大…兔…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.24,0:15:46.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼 不逃了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.13,0:15:49.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微想起我自己是怎樣的人了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.86,0:15:51.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.53,0:15:55.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是超級不愛放棄的一個人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.42,0:15:58.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至今為止都是一直在掙扎著掙扎著
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.30,0:16:01.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最後卻一直都贏了下來
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.89,0:16:04.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最後？那是指的…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.36,0:16:09.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.53,0:16:16.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希梅亞在那裡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.72,0:16:19.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我就一定要把她奪回來
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.53,0:16:22.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,距離最初的死過15分鐘了呀
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.69,0:16:25.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但那又如何
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.60,0:16:29.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還是一樣什麼都做不到吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.50,0:16:33.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽得到嗎 能聽到的吧 希梅亞
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.48,0:16:37.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然扔下你自己跑掉 我辦不到
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.28,0:16:42.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為就算這麼活下去 沒有你的話也就沒有意義了呀
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.45,0:16:46.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安心吧 這就殺你7次
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.87,0:16:54.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然我是笨蛋 在這種狀況還是想不出辦法 但…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.72,0:16:59.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論何時我都會在希梅亞身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.55,0:17:06.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該和她在一起的是我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.08,0:17:11.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無知 無能 無力的你也想保護她？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.14,0:17:18.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那一天 被希梅亞施下魔法的時候發誓了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.19,0:17:20.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發誓了吧 希梅亞
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.52,0:17:25.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發誓不論是生還是死 都永遠在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.82,0:17:31.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鐵大兔 我絕不會原諒你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.31,0:17:38.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作為區區伏在地上的醜陋蛆蟲 卻被她所愛的你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.68,0:17:43.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希梅亞 回答我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.50,0:17:49.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你已經死了5次了 剩下的生命只剩一條
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.69,0:17:51.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會再有下次了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.77,0:17:53.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.81,0:17:56.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對吧 希梅亞
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.77,0:18:00.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,閉嘴 明明是把她弄壞成這樣的罪魁禍首
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.84,0:18:03.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她因對你的愛而瘋狂從而選擇了死亡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.90,0:18:08.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為你的錯 她已經基本沒有時間可活了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.54,0:18:10.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在說什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.19,0:18:19.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保護她？拯救她？別逗我了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.43,0:18:21.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別逗我了 別逗我了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.29,0:18:23.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,殺死了她的不就是你嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.72,0:18:26.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了你這種渣滓她…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.79,0:18:29.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大兔
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.03,0:18:34.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大兔
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.74,0:18:37.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為…為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.09,0:18:40.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希梅亞
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.62,0:18:43.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我這條命為你而存
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.92,0:18:47.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我對希梅亞…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.72,0:18:50.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我對大兔…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.26,0:19:16.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我愛你大兔
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.40,0:19:27.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我僅是為了保護你而生
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.37,0:19:32.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行的 你保護不了我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.88,0:19:35.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能保護我的只有大兔
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.20,0:19:42.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把我創造出來的是你 我為了使你不再寂寞而生
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.35,0:19:45.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…但是我依然很寂寞
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.97,0:19:49.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你沒能填補我的心
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.37,0:19:54.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有大兔填補了我的心
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.49,0:19:58.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有大兔找到了我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.20,0:20:01.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天魔會來
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.51,0:20:06.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天魔會來侵犯失去了力量的你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.42,0:20:13.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那樣一切就都完了 失去了力量的你無法抵擋
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.24,0:20:14.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我的幫助是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.62,0:20:15.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.64,0:20:18.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 巴爾思庫拉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.95,0:20:23.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能在大兔身邊笑著的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.60,0:20:28.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,僅此就好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.85,0:20:34.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 巴爾思庫拉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.87,0:20:39.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.37,0:20:48.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,賽托希梅亞 賽托希梅亞
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.16,0:20:55.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請不要忘記 能保護你的不是鐵大兔
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.90,0:20:58.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而是我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.05,0:21:04.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大兔
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.42,0:21:07.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希梅亞 是希梅亞吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.40,0:21:17.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶 大兔
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.21,0:21:20.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.75,0:21:26.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,X我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.87,0:21:28.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.18,0:21:34.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我的身體融化在你的溫暖中吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.26,0:21:41.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了嘛 大兔
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.63,0:21:46.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點來X我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.72,0:23:23.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼她已經覺醒了？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.00,0:23:24.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.70,0:23:26.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切都與計劃相同？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.59,0:23:27.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.09,0:23:31.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上古魔女賽托希梅亞
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.39,0:23:37.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定要防止她完成神秘魔法<幸福>
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.61,0:23:38.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.71,0:23:42.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是僅為此才被創造出來的 這點…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.41,0:23:43.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.15,0:23:48.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎 你真是坦率的好孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.76,0:23:52.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行了 退下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.69,0:23:55.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,繼續監視吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.98,0:23:56.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.69,0:24:01.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我好痛苦 大兔
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.35,0:24:03.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.64,0:24:09.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我為什麼在這種地方？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.64,0:24:12.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼人類這麼煩呢
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.30,0:24:15.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是大兔之外的人類都去死的話
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.54,0:24:17.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就可以和大兔獨處了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.91,0:24:20.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乾脆用魔法讓人類滅亡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.47,0:24:22.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但那麼幹的話大兔會生氣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.84,0:24:26.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大兔生氣時的表情我也喜歡
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.74,0:24:30.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想到大兔心就開始撲通撲通亂跳了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.25,0:24:33.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然還是滅掉人類吧 因為人家想和大兔獨處
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.13,0:24:38.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我開殺了 下等人類們覺悟吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.01,0:24:39.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,0)\pos(465,120)\1c&H0BFFFF&\3c&HA503A5&\bord2\3a&H3A&\shad1\4c&H8F8F8F&}下集「天魔之名終獲吟誦」
